---
title: Lemony Spaghetti with Chicken Sausage plus Brussels Sprouts, Toasted Panko & Chives
description: For a seamless, stress-free date night, we can’t recommend highly enough this easy yet luxurious and unexpected vegetarian dinner, full of textures and lots of slurping and lip licking opportunities ;). Al dente spaghetti, shredded Brussels sprouts, Parmesan, lemon, and chives come together in a combination that's satisfying, and classically comforting. When you add that sprinkle of chili flakes (spicy!) and toasted panko (crunchy!) over the top you might be going from situationship to relationship before you know it!
